By":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:37:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實老實講句, 屋企阿媽有少少錢, 我一直都係抱住一個唔驚人炒嘅心態去返工, 驚就唔係驚, 但見倒公司成班擦鞋狗出嚟維護一啲明明唔公平嘅制度, 真係覺得好撚噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明明班擦鞋狗都係做緊奴才</blockquote><br />\n我明你感受呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做過幾間飲食 明明大家都係出黎做狗<br />\n點解仲要玩小圈子？<br />\n大家都出係想搵兩餐姐<br />\n但又要做到互篤背脊 擦上司鞋<br />\n<br />\n本身我個人就無咩機心<br />\n唔明做排斥人個邊亦都唔想被排擠<br />\n唯有返工個陣自閉吓啦<br />\n都有諗過有冇邊到係無小圈子呢？<br />\n但無奈 有人嘅地方 就一定有小圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fafbd0fb31c1d4b7c86d7276b186f7a24a5b9d61","tid":484013,"uid":54658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:38:26.000Z","msg":"24歲巴, 就畢業 為搵工煩緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3a6ad9c120b54bf4a47108e56281ff6d76fdca","tid":484013,"uid":113675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:40:02.000Z","msg":"27巴<br />\n<br />\n讀緊Master<br />\n明年出黎都係2x K<br />\n永世追唔到樓價~<br />\n<br />\n仲點溝女"},{"pid":"d68ac98a40eebc66f336c1a86832ccddc35e81f5","tid":484013,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:40:14.000Z","msg":"18 巴<br />\n今年由垃圾band3中中 升左上去hku ba 英文底差讀到好崩潰 冇曬動力冇曬方向讀書 成日又諗起出路問題 結果成個人都好唔開心好頹好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a39fb8e1fc4d0dd4e4062be68d78c89939e7449","tid":484013,"uid":36515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>19巴 讀工程讀到想死 今個sem 個爛硬gpa</blockquote><br />\n你grad個陣係工程低峰<br />\n諗下轉科/轉行</blockquote><br />\n讀緊me 我諗住考海關 入境個d</blockquote><br />\n邊間u <br 